-- ================================================================================ --
-- NEORV32 SoC - Two-Wire Device (TWD)                                              --
-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- --
-- The NEORV32 RISC-V Processor - https://github.com/stnolting/neorv32              --
-- Copyright (c) NEORV32 contributors.                                              --
-- Copyright (c) 2020 - 2025 Stephan Nolting. All rights reserved.                  --
